      "amount": "1 cup"
    },
    {
      "name": "Panko breadcrumbs",
      "amount": "2 cups"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "Slice French bread into thin rounds and lightly toast until golden.",
    "In a pan, sauté minced garlic and onion with olive oil for about 2 minutes.",
    "Add low-sodium soy sauce and water or chicken stock, bring to a simmer. Stir in parsley.",
    "Spread the mixture evenly over each slice of bread, allowing it to cool slightly before crumbling into pieces.",
    "Sprinkle panko breadcrumbs on top of the garlic mixtures, then bake for 10-15 minutes until golden brown and crispy."
